{"id":101864,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/一个来自美国的“天方夜谭”/","date":"2010-08-30T23:52:08Z","modified":"2010-08-30T23:52:08Z","title":"一个来自美国的“天方夜谭”","content":"<p><p align=\"left\"><span>面对惨烈的灾情，出于人类共有的恻隐之心，捐款成了众多善心人的首选。尽管中国大陆慈善业起步很晚，但近几年发展迅速。以汶川地震为例，截至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月，全国共收到民间捐赠资金</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">652.5</span><span>亿元人民币，玉树地震也收到上百亿捐赠。可见，中国慈善业已经成为一股不可忽视的社会力量。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span>慈善一词在希腊语中意为“人类博爱行为”，在古代中国常用“仁义”来表示对弱势群体的帮助。现代社会这种博爱的仁义行为一般体现在两个层面：一是国家制度层面保障公民基本生活需求的社会保障制度，二是社会服务层面的职业化、专业化的慈善工作。相比以往的零星救济，“权利性”取代了“施舍性”、“制度化”代替了“随意性”。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span>救灾、保证灾后灾民的基本生活 ……</p>\n<p>……</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><strong><span><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p></span></span></strong><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span></p>\n<p><span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p>“要翻墙，<a href=\"http://idiaoyuzhifa.info\" target=\"_blank\">用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[8800]}